  <li>Lectures on Property testing


    
   <div
      style="line-height:1.5em;font-size:.9em;color:#848484;padding-top:.5em;padding-left:1em">



    <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/002200009390044W"><u>Self-testing/correcting with applications to numerical problems</u></a>, Manuel Blum, Michael Luby, Ronitt Rubinfeld
